{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "0203c0bb-addd-4b15-97f5-c1062906e807", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0203c0bb-addd-4b15-97f5-c1062906e807@3.pkg/1772595199787/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772595200042", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0203c0bb-addd-4b15-97f5-c1062906e807@3.pkg/1772595199787/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772595200042"}, "identifier": "0203c0bb-addd-4b15-97f5-c1062906e807", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>结合语境思考</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>1. “窗子打开了，她面前是一朵盛开的、紫色的豌豆花。小女孩低下头来，轻轻地吻了一下它柔嫩的叶子。这一天简直像一个节日。”为什么说“这一天简直像一个节日”？下列理解正确的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "1. “窗子打开了，她面前是一朵盛开的、紫色的豌豆花。小女孩低下头来，轻轻地吻了一下它柔嫩的叶子。这一天简直像一个节日。”为什么说“这一天简直像一个节日”？下列理解正确的一项是（       ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0203c0bb-addd-4b15-97f5-c1062906e807@3.pkg/item.json?v=1747559442328", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>节日里总是鲜花盛开，现在豌豆花开了，所以“简直像一个节日”。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>孩子在节日里总是快乐的，小姑娘在那一天特别高兴，所以说“简直像一个节日”。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>小姑娘受到豌豆顽强的生命力的鼓舞，终于能够坐起来，并且快乐地生活，母亲也对生活充满了希望，所以说“简直像一个节日”。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>豌豆从落到窗台到发芽，展示着顽强的生命力，今天它终于开花了，所以说“简直像一个节日”。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>1. “窗子打开了，她面前是一朵盛开的、紫色的豌豆花。小女孩低下头来，轻轻地吻了一下它柔嫩的叶子。这一天简直像一个节日。”为什么说“这一天简直像一个节日”？下列理解正确的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbd3ea-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "$RE0200", "5036342748", "44beb9aa-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0201", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbd3ea-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "44beb9aa-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "0203c0bb-addd-4b15-97f5-c1062906e807", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "1. “窗子打开了，她面前是一朵盛开的、紫色的豌豆花。小女孩低下头来，轻轻地吻了一下它柔嫩的叶子。这一天简直像一个节日。”为什么说“这一天简直像一个节日”？下列理解正确的一项是（       ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>1. “窗子打开了，她面前是一朵盛开的、紫色的豌豆花。小女孩低下头来，轻轻地吻了一下它柔嫩的叶子。这一天简直像一个节日。”为什么说“这一天简直像一个节日”？下列理解正确的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "gl